imr.media.midi

Class MIDIMetaEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • imr.media.midi.MIDIEvent
      • imr.media.midi.MIDIMetaEvent

  • public final class MIDIMetaEvent
extends MIDIEvent
    A MIDIMetaEvent extends MIDIEvent So it has, a MIDIMessage and a time stamp in ticks. In addition a MIDIMetaEvent has a byte array with additional data.
    See Also:
    MIDIEvent, MIDIMessage
